episodes.title: Another True Crime Podcast: The Family (Episode 4)
episodes.description: Welcome to Another True Crime Podcast, a How Did We Get Here Productions production. In this episode Nani tells Nova the worst story they have ever heard. They talk all about one of the worst cults in Australia, The Family. Their leader, Anne Hamilton-Byrne, believed she was Jesus, stole babies, and the cult is still active! What's scarier than all that? Anne's receding hair line.Podcast art made by our very own Nova!We have a Patreon! Higher tier paying Patrons get early access to the podcast.
